      • composite

        public String composite(String formatKey,
               String joiner,
               Object objectToInvokeMethodOn)
        A property that is composed of other properties.

        It firstly fetches the formatKey using fetch(String). It will proceed to convert the returned properties from the fetch(String) method to a methodName and invoke this method against the object passed in. Finally, concatenation occurs with the return values of the methods using the joiner parameter as a separator.
